sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client
    participant R as VllmPDRouter
    participant P as Prefill实例
    participant P_ZMQ as Prefill SendingThread<br/>(ZMQ ROUTER)
    participant TE as Mooncake RDMA
    participant D as Decode实例
    participant D_ZMQ as Decode RecvingThread

    rect rgb(230,245,255)
    Note over R,D_ZMQ: ===== 初始化阶段 =====

    Note over R: 注册Prefill/Decode到WorkerRegistry(无ZMQ服务发现)
    R->>P: GET /health (启动等待直到返回200)
    P-->>R: 200 OK
    R->>D: GET /health (启动等待直到返回200)
    D-->>R: 200 OK

    R->>P: GET /query (Mooncake bootstrap)
    P-->>R: {dp_rank: {engine_id: "xxx"}}
    Note over R: 缓存MooncakePrefillInfo

    Note over P: register_kv_caches(): 注册KV内存到TransferEngine
    Note over P: 启动SendingThread(ZMQ ROUTER监听)
    Note over D: register_kv_caches(): 注册KV内存到TransferEngine
    Note over D: 启动RecvingThread
    Note over R: start_health_checker(): 后台周期检查线程
    end

    rect rgb(255,250,230)
    Note over R,D_ZMQ: ===== 后台健康检查(每30-60s) =====

    loop 每 check_interval_secs
        R->>P: GET /health
        P-->>R: 200 OK / 超时
        R->>D: GET /health
        D-->>R: 200 OK / 超时
        Note over R: 连续失败>=3次 -> set_healthy(false)
        Note over R: 连续成功>=2次 -> set_healthy(true)
    end
    end

    rect rgb(245,240,255)
    Note over C,D_ZMQ: ===== 请求处理 =====

    C->>R: POST /v1/chat/completions

    Note over R: 同时选择Prefill和Decode实例(请求发送前)
    Note over R: prefill_policy.select_worker() -> P
    Note over R: decode_policy.select_worker() -> D
    Note over R: 过滤: is_available() = is_healthy() AND 熔断器可用

    Note over R: 构建Prefill请求: max_tokens=1, stream=false
    Note over R: kv_transfer_params={do_remote_decode:true, transfer_id}

    R->>P: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(max_tokens=1, kv_transfer_params)

    Note over P: Prefill计算: token embedding + 全部Transformer层
    Note over P: 生成KV Cache, 输出1个token

    P-->>R: 200 {kv_transfer_params: {<br/>remote_block_ids, remote_engine_id,<br/>remote_host, remote_port,<br/>remote_request_id, last_token_id}}

    Note over R: 释放prefill负载
    Note over R: 构建Decode请求: 附加prefill返回的kv_transfer_params

    R->>D: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(原始max_tokens, kv_transfer_params={do_remote_prefill:true, remote_host/port/block_ids})

    Note over D: 分配KV Cache blocks
    Note over D: start_load_kv() -> 向RecvingThread提交拉取任务

    D_ZMQ->>P_ZMQ: ZMQ GET_META_MSG
    P_ZMQ-->>D_ZMQ: ZMQ MooncakeAgentMetadata<br/>(base_addr, te_rpc_port, block_lens)

    D_ZMQ->>TE: batch_transfer_sync_read<br/>(RDMA PULL: D从P拉取KV Cache)
    TE-->>D_ZMQ: 传输完成

    D_ZMQ->>P_ZMQ: ZMQ DONE_RECVING_MSG
    Note over P: 收到通知,释放KV Cache blocks

    Note over D: KV加载完成,跳过prefill,开始逐token decode

    loop 逐token流式输出
        D-->>R: Stream chunk
        R-->>C: SSE data
    end

    D-->>R: [DONE]
    R-->>C: [DONE]

    Note over R: 释放decode负载, 记录请求结果到熔断器
    end
